# Q4. Find Pods Terminated First

### Question

Check all Pods in Namespace `project-c13`.

Find Pods that would probably be terminated first if nodes run out of CPU or memory.

Write names to:

```bash
/opt/course/4/pods-terminated-first.txt
```

### Fast Search

```text
pod qos class
```

### Solution

Check QoS:

```bash
kubectl get pod -n project-c13 \
-o custom-columns=NAME:.metadata.name,QOS:.status.qosClass
```

Pods with:

```text
BestEffort
```

will be terminated first.

Write their names:

```bash
echo pod-name > /opt/course/4/pods-terminated-first.txt
```

