# Q6. PV PVC Deployment

### Question

Create:

PV:

```text
safari-pv
```

* 2Gi
* RWO
* hostPath=/Volumes/Data
* no StorageClass

PVC:

```text
safari-pvc
```

Namespace:

```text
project-t230
```

Deployment:

```text
safari
```

Image:

```text
httpd:2-alpine
```

Mount:

```text
/tmp/safari-data
```

### Fast Search

```text
hostpath persistent volume
```

### Solution

PV:

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolume
metadata:
  name: safari-pv
spec:
  capacity:
    storage: 2Gi
  accessModes:
  - ReadWriteOnce
  storageClassName: ""
  hostPath:
    path: /Volumes/Data
```

PVC:

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolumeClaim
metadata:
  name: safari-pvc
  namespace: project-t230
spec:
  accessModes:
  - ReadWriteOnce
  resources:
    requests:
      storage: 2Gi
  storageClassName: ""
```

Deployment mount:

```yaml
volumeMounts:
- mountPath: /tmp/safari-data
  name: safari-storage

volumes:
- name: safari-storage
  persistentVolumeClaim:
    claimName: safari-pvc
```

