```bash
kubectl get nodes
```

SSH:

```bash
ssh cka3962-node1
```

Install matching version:

```bash
apt-cache madison kubeadm
```

```bash
apt install kubeadm=<VERSION>
apt install kubelet=<VERSION>
kubectl=<VERSION>
```

Join command:

```bash
kubeadm token create --print-join-command
```

Run join command on worker.

